{"tid":1395164,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小妹比人問黎緊星期六有咩做...點答好","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:41:31.000Z","uid":137043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"344236cb66afaaa50086b98742aead39712611d7","tid":1395164,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"黎緊星期六8月3，我約左好多人喺大角咀晏架街足球場準備去行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢次小妹終於有著落，唔洗再自己一個岀去9fingfing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚大家唔識去跟住甩我底，下面比哂搭車行路方法比大家，唔準放我飛機啊！我嬲會發脾氣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記住帶啲糧食同防具，嗰邊好多舊樓同狗，驚陣間行行下有野從天而降整親大家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多，到時見喇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxsRja9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoxsRja9.png&h=76c45619&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D6SFcwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD6SFcwa.png&h=10e11cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcVWvhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcVWvhQ.png&h=a79ee754&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g35oahR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg35oahR.png&h=fabb836d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PF0vzKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPF0vzKy.png&h=1e4d95a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93638636bf4ce284286657f4255feb79e7268189","tid":1395164,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"再唔識路我可以帶大家去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9476f9a4885217d5b02ba62812017b9019fdb52f","tid":1395164,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"有無人可以善意回覆下我啊"},